Subject: Re: [VB] front tranny mount

Don't forget to check the reduction box to spring
plate bolts for proper torque.  I just had those
loosen up on me in the doublecab a couple weeks ago. 
This can sound like fulcrum plates/motor mounts/bad
drum or axle splines.

